casebody.data:
S.D., a Minor, By His Parents and Natural Guardians, A.D. and R.D., et al., petitioners,
v.
HADDON HEIGHTS BOARD OF EDUCATION. No. 16-1054. Supreme Court of the United States May 15, 2017.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit for further consideration in light of Fry v. Napoleon *2122Community Schools, 580 U.S. ----, 137 S.Ct. 743, 197 L.Ed.2d 46 (2017).
